# Local development: leave both blank and the app will use a local SQLite
# file (local.db) via libSQL's file:// mode. No signup needed to run `npm run dev`.
#
# Production (Vercel): create a free Turso database (https://turso.tech) and
# paste its credentials here / into Vercel's Environment Variables UI.
#   turso db create economics-blog
#   turso db show economics-blog --url
#   turso db tokens create economics-blog
TURSO_DATABASE_URL=
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=
